message.text:
𝑴𝑬𝑴𝑩𝑬𝑹𝑺𝑯𝑰𝑷 𝑨𝑷𝑷𝑳𝑰𝑪𝑨𝑻𝑰𝑶𝑵 | 𝑪𝑶𝑵𝑭𝑰𝑹𝑴𝑨𝑻𝑰𝑶𝑵 𝑬𝑴𝑨𝑰𝑳 𝑺𝑬𝑵𝑻!

Heads up to all our aspiring student-volunteers! 

In line with our membership application process, the Confirmation Emails have officially been sent out yesterday, 15 September 2025, to your respective FEU Outlook Emails.

Check your emails now and duly accomplish our Confirmation Form to secure your membership within Tamaraw Volunteers-Manila! Membership Confirmation will only be open until TOMORROW, 17 September 2025!

Confirm now! We can't wait for you to get on board with the TAMVOL Fam!

#AltruismAboveAndBeyond
#ActionOnTheGround

message.text:
𝑴𝑬𝑴𝑩𝑬𝑹𝑺𝑯𝑰𝑷 𝑨𝑷𝑷𝑳𝑰𝑪𝑨𝑻𝑰𝑶𝑵 | 𝑪𝑶𝑵𝑭𝑰𝑹𝑴𝑨𝑻𝑰𝑶𝑵 𝑬𝑴𝑨𝑰𝑳 𝑺𝑬𝑵𝑻!

Heads up to all our aspiring student-volunteers! 

In line with our membership application process, the Confirmation Emails have officially been sent out yesterday, 15 September 2025, to your respective FEU Outlook Emails.

Check your emails now and duly accomplish our Confirmation Form to secure your membership within Tamaraw Volunteers-Manila! Membership Confirmation will only be open until TOMORROW, 17 September 2025!

Confirm now! We can't wait for you to get on board with the TAMVOL Fam!

#AltruismAboveAndBeyond
#ActionOnTheGround
